VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(disable|bypass|ignore|suppress|unsafe)\b
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(auth|csrf|xss|cors|tls|ssl|verify|validation|sanitize|security) && MISSING:(example|sample|dummy|test|placeholder)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects weak or inadequate security mitigations.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Weak Mitigation: Using disable|bypass|ignore|suppress|unsafe.
